Text:
Hello Mr. Boerner . My name is Abigail Kinney. I am a freshman journalism major at Kent State University. For my final in one of my journalism courses we have to write a featured article about an interesting person, business, or event. After talking with one of my professors, Mr. Oleg Lougheed was so gracious to let me interview him. We are required to have two additional sources in our article. Mr. Lougheed forwarded me your contact information. If you are able to, I would greatly appreciate it if I could set up a phone interview with you to be one of my sources?
Thank you 
Abigail L Kinney
Hi Abigail. I’m free tomorrow 10am - 3pm EST. Would 30 minutes in that timeframe work for you?
Yes, 30 minutes is perfect. Is 1:30  good?
yes. You can call my cell then. I’m flexible. Thanks!

I greatly appreciate it. I have attached a copy of the article if you wanted to read it.
 Thanks again.
